OL,3,CBeing called 'weirdo' by colleague is
OL,4,Ca 'violation of dignity', tribunal
OL,5,Crules
OL,7,F"In the circumstances, we were
OL,8,Fsatisfied that the comments did
OL,9,Finvolve unwanted conduct which had the
OL,10,Feffect of violating the claimant's
OL,11,Fdignity."
OL,13,FThe Venture was ordered to pay Mr
OL,14,FJames #17,154.86 in compensation,
OL,15,Fincluding #15,000 for injury to
OL,16,Ffeelings, after the judge partly
OL,17,Fupheld his complaints of disability
OL,18,Fdiscrimination and failure to make
OL,19,Freasonable adjustments.
