OL,5,Crules
OL,7,FThe judge said: "The discussion
OL,8,Finvolved around Mr King's own concerns
OL,9,Fthat the claimant's work and care for
OL,10,Fchildren would be impacted by his
OL,11,Fmental health situation, and we felt
OL,12,Fthat that concern was trivialised by
OL,13,FMr King's comparison of that with
OL,14,Fsomeone attending work suffering with
OL,15,Fa hangover."
OL,17,FThe Venture provides a range of
OL,18,Fcommunity-based services, primarily
OL,19,Ffor the benefit of children and young
OL,20,Fpeople.
